    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778840/extras/01c4d69af7c869f222f34df43f29bbf5.avif?t=1765288063\" width=600 height=280 /></span><br><br>在一片残垣断壁的古老世界中，踏上一只孤独的狐狸背井离乡的旅程。 在睿智的乌鸦同伴的帮助下，寻找失落的传奇守护者，并将他们从黑暗萨满格里姆尼尔的手中解救出来。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778840/extras/45ffbfe1ba808f71beca4ab5503b67de.webp?t=1765288063\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778840/extras/7de7a1d8638a851e75ef6dd188c18f5b.avif?t=1765288063\" width=600 height=280 /></span><br><br>在广阔而古老的开放世界中不羁漫游，探索被遗忘的漫长历史。探索独特而美丽的生物群落，了解他们所面临的挑战，并揭开他们的秘密。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778840/extras/45ffbfe1ba808f71beca4ab5503b67de.webp?t=1765288063\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778840/extras/8b43afa94f16519ff2b4254efa6541b1.avif?t=1765288063\" width=600 height=280 /></span><br><br>发现强大的符文，增强你的能力，穿越葱茏茂密的森林和白雪皑皑的山峰，探索黑暗而古老的墓穴，以拯救失落的守护者。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778840/extras/5c632aebda3f52f5ebf036a4a106e24e.avif?t=1765288063\" width=600 height=407 /></span><br><br>定制狐狸的外观和技能，以匹配你的游戏风格，使每次游戏体验都独一无二。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778840/extras/45ffbfe1ba808f71beca4ab5503b67de.webp?t=1765288063\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778840/extras/4b9188dd306f06666954ef211fb45a5b.avif?t=1765288063\" width=600 height=280 /></span><br><br>在惊心动魄的遭遇中解开谜题，直面强大的敌人，拯救传奇的守护兽。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1778840/extras/240019dfc35cce0ae7e4b47202941e09.webp?t=1765288063\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>通过丰富多样的定制选项创造你自己的独特狐狸。<br></li><li>探索跨越不同地区的绚丽开放世界。<br></li><li>在传奇的邂逅中净化黑化的守护者。<br></li><li>获得克服挑战的新能力。<br></li><li>寻找强大的符文来增强你的能力。<br></li><li>在一场鼓舞人心的全新冒险中延续《Spirit of the North》的美丽和传说。</li></ul>",
